high_descs: take a few steps forward and turn to the right
pick up the yellow handle knife from the table
turn to the right and go forward past clear the table and turn to the left and take a step and turn to the right and go to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and slice with the knife the potato on the top shelf left of the apple and close the door
turn to the right and take a few steps and turn to the left facing the stove
put the knife in the pot on the back of the stove
turn to the left and take a few steps and turn to the right facing the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and take a slice of potato on the top shelf left of the apple and close the door
turn to the right and take a few steps and turn to the left facing the stove
put the potato slice in the pot right of the knife on the back of the stove
pick up the pot with the knife and potato slice in it from the stove
turn to the right twice and go to the door and turn to the left and go to the table
put the the pot with the knife and potato slice in it on back of the table
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a knife and a potato slice in it on a table

high_descs: Turn to the white table on the right.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the table.
Turn to the right, go to the fridge on the other side of the room.
Open the fridge, cut the potato on the top shelf of the fridge into slices.
Turn to the right, go to the stove that is on the left.
Put the knife into the pot on the back left burner of the stove.
Turn to the left, go to the fridge that is on the right.
Remove a slice of potato from the fridge.
Turn to the right, go to the stove that is on the left.
Put the slice of potato into the pot on the back left burner of the stove.
Pick up the pot that contains the knife and potato from the stove.
Turn around, go to the door, hang a left and go to the round black table.
Put the pot on the table behind the salt.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot containing potato and a knife on a table.
